"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-11-Farewell-to-veteran-athletes-who-have-competed-at-their-final-Olympics-1vYEUWwyiWY-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  With the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics set to close on Sunday evening, many athletes have already taken their final bows at the multisport competition.  Ma Long of China competes in the men's team table tennis final against Sweden at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 9, 2024. /CFP  Timo Boll of Germany waves at supporters after competing in the men's team table tennis quarterfinals against Sweden at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 6, 2024. /CFP  Andy Murray of Great Britain reacts after hitting a winner in the men's doubles tennis quarterfinals with Daniel Evans against Tommy Paul and Taylor Fritz of the USA at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 1, 2024. /CFP  Angelique Kerber of Germany competes in the women's singles tennis quarterfinals against Zheng Qinwen of China at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, July 31, 2024. /CFP  Eliud Kipchoge (C) of Kenya competes in the men's marathon at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 10, 2024. /CFP  Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce of Jamaica competes in the women's 100-meter preliminaries at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 2, 2024. /CFP  Gong Lijiao of China competes in the women's shot put final at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 9, 2024. /CFP  Shi Zhiyong of China competes in the men's 73-kilogram weightlifting final at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 8, 2024. /CFP  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: